                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I lost my 1st 3 because I was using "normal" tactics in "hard"
<br />

<br />
I was the mezzer and slower -- and we did not have FD in the group.
<br />

<br />
- enchanters should NOT pull
<br />
- dont bother with lull  (its only going to get you killed with resists)
<br />

<br />

<br />
my personal thoughts on winning HARD LDoN is ...
<br />
need 
<br />
- FD or Slower (BST/Shammy)
<br />
- Mezzer  (Chanter/Bard)
<br />
- good tank
<br />

<br />
from my experiences, 
<br />
- with no FD, the MT should be puller
<br />
- mezzer should have pretargets
<br />
(otherwise, use FD pulls to get less mobs)
<br />

<br />
you really need these beasties SLOWED asap,
<br />
its very risky to have one person doing both mezzes and slows if many are in camp.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">charm</span> helps alot for DPS
<br />
(a chanter cannot charm an even con tho)
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">and dont forget !</span>
<br />
you can have 2 pretargets using the "Switch between targets" key
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://pub130.ezboard.com/feqasylumenchanter.showMessage?topicID=1289.topic" target="_blank">http://pub130.ezboard.com/feqasylumenchanter.showMessage?topicID=1289.topic</a>
<br />
Open up your options menu and switch to the keymap tab, then select "Targeting" in the pull down menu. 
<br />

<br />
You'll find a new feature, that isn't mapped to a key, called "Switch between targets".</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=81508" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Nadia Nightengale</a> 65 Enchantress
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=582516" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Tassa</a> 65 Paladin
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g28&menustr=080000000000" target="_blank" class="postlink">EQ Traders recipes</a>
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://pub45.ezboard.com/botherworlds31279" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-style: italic"><span style="font-weight: bold">Other Worlds</span></span></a> Nadia's GameNews messageboard</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
