                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Actually thats a great point dess i cant believe i forgot to mention that. In huge rooms many times i will send pet in and mez when the puller dies or something.
<br />

<br />
However I wouldnt rely on this type of pulling for you group when you are getting the group together in the 1st place. You might not get a pet right away. Plus if you send in pet to a room with 4 mobs and charm breaks right after it goes in there...well youre in for a world of hurt hehe.
<br />

<br />
Use this method of pulling as a tool when you are feeling good about your charm lasting. Its kind of an advanced tactic tho so proceed with caution.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
