                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Great Guide Vizier! Thanks.
<br />
And thanks Desseray I'll be trying the pet pulling method soon.
<br />

<br />
My guild is pre-elemental. I'm on 4500 HP buffed. I've just recently started into Hard LDoN and I've succeeded on the last 4.
<br />

<br />
So far my choice on Puller is a SK. SK root snare means I can slow without aggro straight up (but i generally tash then slow which gets aggro briefly). If I do aggro that mob it's snared so I can kite. Preferably there is a Beastlord or Shaman as slower anyway.
<br />
On the last hard in Mir with a SK and Monk they single pulled the whole adventure and I didn't cast Mezz except to try and interrupt CH. 
<br />
On a 2 pull the snared mob comes in slow, the add appears with the SK for easy targeting and the cleric is clear to heal you if it resists mezz as the 'main' fight hasn't started yet.
<br />
I've been doing Hard without a charmed pet mostly because there hasn't been a charm candidate till we're well through. So I've had Insanity up in place of CoD until a target shows up. Plenty of time to load CoD while Bliss/Sleep is running.
<br />

<br />
Check the Cleric has Divine Arbitration - A life saver!
<br />

<br />
Group Makeup
<br />
Puller - SK Preferred, 
<br />
MA - SK/Pally/Warrior with aggro proc weapons
<br />
Primary Slower - Beastlord/Shaman
<br />
Healer - Cleric with DA
<br />
CC - You <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />
<br />
6th - Free
<br />

<br />
Nice to have people with root and snare for resists or secondary crowd control.
<br />

<br />
* * * * * * * 
<br />
Is it worth it? Hell yes !
<br />
You get 105 Adventure points in place of 51. You get great xp from high blue or white con mobs. You get great drops - the stat Augs are +7 rather than +6 and the items off the named are very nice for the pre-Elemental Enchanter. For example in Rujarkian Hills you might get:
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Battle-Torn Cloak of the Ages </span>
<br />
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP 
<br />
Weight: 0.7 Size: MEDIUM 
<br />
Slot: BACK 
<br />
AC: +13 Sta: +10 Wis: +10 Int: +10 Fire Resist: +12 Cold Resist: +8 HP: +70 Mana: +95 
<br />
Classes: Cleric Druid Shaman Wizard Magician Enchanter Necromancer 
<br />
Races: All Races 
<br />
Slot 1: Type 1 
<br />
------------------------------------
<br />
Effect: <span style="font-weight: bold">Flowing Thought II</span>
<br />

<br />
My Guild raids mobs for FT2 items - and this just drops off a named in LDoN? Awesome!</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
