                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm the crazy enchanter (Iumuno would agree with that ... here pet pet I got a weapon for you!)  but some things I do now, and would do even if I had 4.5k hp.
<br />

<br />
Give the pet two weapons, give it your best haste.  If you trust your cleric at all, or trust the wizard to hit exodus just stay back from your pet.  A hasted duel wielding pet has made it where mobs were dieing so quickly that I stopped slowing. (Yeah I tend to slow and cc in hards).
<br />

<br />
We're talking the slow landing at 25% casted on incoming.  The pets are really good dps, quads for 900 whenever you give it two weapons.  Now of course that's going to be very rough on your life, but its liveable.  Just gotta learn where you can be at or have a dedicated healer for you.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
